Body: You need to break the problem down to something you can solve ,  is the message getting to topic?, is the lambda function being triggered?  Is the lambda function generating errors? Is the email being filtered?

When I push Reset button on ESP, I can see the Topic activity as, Thing connected, thing disconnected, thing subscribed and one more time thing subscribed. But when I push boot button on ESP, nothing happens apart from the log message I just posted. https://imgur.com/a/4Fzac Is what I see in Lambda function. Sorry, I am really new to this whole AWS and mongoose environment so still figuring out the debugging.
